lead_paragraph: A surge in applications for PreCheck, the Transportation Security Administration’s solution to long lines, has led to processing delays and enrollment waiting lists.

headline.print_headline: Looking for a Way to Get Through Airport Security More Quickly? Just Get in Line
headline.main: Trying to Get Past Airport Security Faster? Get in Line

snippet: A surge in applications for PreCheck, the Transportation Security Administration’s solution to long lines, has led to processing delays and enrollment waiting lists.
abstract: Transportation Security Admin and officials at MorphoTrust USA, company that administers PreCheck program that allows people to move through airport security more quickly, are working to accelerate program's approval process; spike in applications has left agency and company flat-footed.
